rules.7:
Use the code formatting of discord, it's easier for us to read you like this:
\`\`\`cpp
#include <iostream>
int main()
{
	std::cout << "Hello World" << std::endl;
}
\`\`\`
 ->
```cpp
#include <iostream>
int main()
{
	std::cout << "Hello World" << std::endl;
}
```
Additionally, code should be written in *English* and *english* only
